### [1.0.0] - 2026-01-15
**The "Porches" Launch**
- **Core Engine:** Completed the "Binary Pulse" random number generation logic.
- **UI/UX:** Implemented the "Hacker Green" terminal aesthetic with high-contrast alerts.
- **Audio:** Added dynamic frequency feedback (different tones for High/Low guesses).
- **Branding:** Officially titled the project "The 100th Cipher of [Porches]."
- **Optimization:** Integrated auto-centering title logic to fit standard 80-character displays.

### [Roadmap] - Future Updates
- [ ] **Hard Mode:** Expanding frequency range to 1-500.
- [ ] **Lockout Timer:** Adding a countdown to increase pressure.
- [ ] **Data Persistence:** Saving the lowest "Number of Attempts" as a High Score.

                                               
